caption: b"Still scrolling at this hour? Now's the perfect time to check out our #BlackFriday travel deals and plan your next trip. Link to deals in bio!"
b'From our family to yours, have a safe, healthy and happy #Thanksgiving.'

b'This #Thanksgiving, the #AATeam in Chicago is showing its gratitude for the local community, by ensuring families in need have a special meal to celebrate the holiday. Read the story on our newsroom \xe2\x80\x94 link in bio. #LetGoodTakeFlight'
b'From takeoff to touchdown, learn how our team is taking care of :american_football: teams who travel with us every step of the way. Check out the story in our newsroom!'

b"Every penny counts to Beth Callahan and her colleagues who collect spare change for @UNICEF's Change for Good program. Since 1994, the #AAteam has collected more than $17 million to help vulnerable children worldwide. On #WorldChildrensDay, join us in supporting UNICEF. Link to newsroom in bio."
b"Here's something to look forward to in 2021: More #AAdvantage benefits are en route, whether you're flying with us or our friends on the West Coast, @AlaskaAir. Link to newsroom in bio."
b'Farewell, fees! We\xe2\x80\x99re providing more flexibility for our customers to make travel easier. Link in bio to newsroom for more information!'
b'According to Bloomberg, research paints a clear picture: With protocols and measures in place, travelers should feel confident about flying. https://bit.ly/AAFF_1'

b'The best part of virtual events? Snagging the best seat in the house... American Airlines #AAdvantage @Mastercard holders, grab your complimentary tickets to a virtual acoustic concert with @BebeRexha, presented by yours truly and Mastercard, on @LiveXLive. Link to details and tickets in bio.'
b'Now arriving: more Admirals Clubs reopening. Not a member? Treat yourself with a day pass or become a member. Click the Admirals Club link in bio.'

b'Effective COVID-19 testing of customers traveling, instead of imposing quarantine, is the safest and most efficient way to get the world flying again.\n\nTogether with @oneworld and @British_Airways, our customers traveling from Dallas-Fort Worth, New York and Los Angeles to the UK will be invited to take part in this new COVID-19 testing trial. #testingmustfly'
b'Turn that virtual background into a real one. Wherever you want to work, let us take you there. Check out the "Where to next?" link in bio.'

b'Now you can travel comfortably knowing that you\xe2\x80\x99ve completed everything on your international preflight checklist \xe2\x80\x94 thanks to our partnership with VeriFLY. Learn more in our newsroom.'
b'Our mutli-layered #CleanCommitment, which includes HEPA filters, face coverings and disinfected planes, will help you travel with confidence. https://bit.ly/HarvardAviation'

b'Happy Veterans Day! While we honor them every day, today is dedicated to celebrating those who have served and defended the United States of America, just like Derek Davidson. Derek served in the Air Force for 20 years before joining the #AATeam as a flight crew training instructor. Read his story in our Newsroom.'
b"The special touch we've put on your travel experience is actually a touchless one. :winking_face: #CleanCommitment"
b'Now boarding: Your #holiday cinema in the sky. Relax, unwind and get into the holiday spirit in flight with new, featured FREE movies playing now. Link to newsroom in bio.'
b'Talk about a breath of fresh air\xe2\x80\xa6fast! http://bit.ly/AA_IATAStudy'
b"Your next getaway awaits! Plan the trip you've been dreaming of this year. #LetsGoThere"
b'Ready to reconnect with loved ones? Our Clean Commitment has you covered this holiday season. Link to newsroom in bio.'

b'Surprise your friends, family or closest inner circle with a trip to one of these great destinations. Added Bonus: American now offers preflight testing options to more destinations than any other U.S. carrier through a partnership with @LetsGetChecked. Link to newsroom in bio.'
b"Today's the day. If you haven't already, #vote. :ballot_box_with_ballot:"

b'This holiday season is about connecting with friends and loved ones in the place you call home. From welcome aboard to welcome home, #YouAreWhyWeFly. Click the Travel Home for the Holidays link in bio.'
b'Traveling this #Halloween? Have a gourd time and wear a face covering!'
b'Traveling with confidence starts with factual flying. Check out these facts!'

b'These aren\xe2\x80\x99t your typical ghost towns. Check out these spooky cities where you\xe2\x80\x99re sure to meet a friendly spirit. :ghost: #Halloween2020 :jack-o-lantern: Link to American Way in bio.'
b"As colder weather approaches, we're taking you from bored to board. Check out a few of our favorite slopes, where you're sure to catch some fresh mountain air. Link in bio."
b"HEP-HEP-A-Ray for HEPA filters! We\xe2\x80\x99ve been purifying the air on our fleet since the '90s, so clean air is something we can all cheer about. https://bit.ly/AADYK_3"
b'Breathe in. Breathe out. Breathe easy. HEPA\xe2\x80\x99s got your back (and all the nasty stuff). http://bit.ly/AAFF_3'
b"You're never fully dressed without a mask. Plus it helps slow the spread of #COVID19."
b"Traveling with us? Don't forget to wear your mask from Point A to Point B. And everywhere in between. https://bit.ly/AAFF_8"
b'When you spot your face on the mag inside the seatback. Check out the latest in American Way online (or book a trip :winking_face:). Link in bio.'
b'Noodling where to go next? Get inspired by #NationalPastaDay.'
b'The timer is set, let\xe2\x80\x99s wash for 20 seconds! #GlobalHandwashingDay2020'

b"Growing up in San Juan, Puerto Rico, #AATeam member Carlos Jimenez discovered his passion for aviation at a young age. In honor of #HispanicHeritageMonth, we\xe2\x80\x99re celebrating Carlos and his journey with us at American. Read Carlos' story in our newsroom, link in bio."

b'Ever wonder what a million miles would look like in your AAdvantage account? Here is one way to find out. Enter our Million Miles Closer Sweepstakes for a chance to win one million AAdvantage miles \xe2\x80\x94 link in bio.'
b'Stop, guac and roll \xe2\x80\x94 guacamole has returned to select Admirals Club lounges. Pro Tip: Add some fresh jalape\xc3\xb1os, it\xe2\x80\x99s :fire:.'

b'It\xe2\x80\x99s #ThrowbackThursday, so we had to #tbt to one of our faves \xe2\x80\x94 the MD-80! Today, we want to know \xe2\x80\xa6 which #Super80 are you? Comment below!

A. Watch the sunset.
B. Go on an excursion.
C. Hit the slopes.
D. I like the night life, baby!'

b"When Karen Churchill was diagnosed with breast cancer in 2017, the #AAteam stepped in to do what they do best \xe2\x80\x94 care for people on life's journey. Read Karen's story in our newsroom \xe2\x80\x94 link in bio. #BreastCancerAwarenessMonth"

b'Our Customer Service #AATeam members go above and beyond to care for our customers. During #NationalCustomerServiceWeek, we recognize their efforts and show our appreciation for all that they do each and every day.'

b'Dream big (like Boeing 787 Dreamliner big!). To celebrate Girls in Aviation Day, our #AATeam First Officer Christine Albertson took a group of aspiring aviators on a behind-the-scenes tour of her office.'
b'We think you really autumn know about these low fares for fall. Visit our Fall Flight Deals link in bio. #YouAreWhyWeFly'

b"Got the new iOS? App Clips and widgets are now available for our mobile app. It\xe2\x80\x99s now easier to get your travel details at a quick glance, leaving you more time to focus on your travel pics. Now, that's an upgrade."
